components.name: Check PCD SFTP Folder
components.description: Verify SFTP folder availability and contents before starting ETL process
outputs: Folder status verification for downstream processing

components.name: Check PCD Shared Folder
components.description: Validate shared folder accessibility after SFTP check
inputs: Folder status verification for downstream processing
outputs: Shared folder status for data extraction phase

upstream_policy.description: Depends on successful completion of Check PCD SFTP Folder

components.name: Start PCD Extract 1
components.description: Synchronization point after folder checks, initiates parallel API extraction
inputs: Shared folder status for data extraction phase
outputs: Triggers parallel HTTP API extraction tasks

upstream_policy.description: Depends on successful completion of Check PCD Shared Folder

components.name: Parallel HTTP API Extraction
components.description: Extract PCD data from various healthcare system APIs in parallel
inputs: Triggers parallel HTTP API extraction tasks
outputs: API response data with statusCode 200 validation

upstream_policy.description: Depends on successful completion of Start PCD Extract 1

components.name: Start PCD Extract 2
components.description: Synchronization point after Status_Tracker API call completion
inputs: API response data with statusCode 200 validation
outputs: Signals readiness for file upload processing

upstream_policy.description: Depends on successful completion of Parallel HTTP API Extraction

components.name: PCD File Upload
components.description: Execute main ETL job to process and upload extracted PCD data
inputs: API response data with statusCode 200 validation
Signals readiness for file upload processing

upstream_policy.description: Depends on successful completion of Start PCD Extract 2 and Parallel HTTP API Extraction

components.name: ETL Notification
components.description: Send comprehensive email notifications with success/failure status and failed task details
inputs: All upstream task completion (success or failure)
outputs: Email notifications to appropriate distribution lists

upstream_policy.description: Always executes regardless of upstream success/failure
